snippet.title: Harrison Divecha
snippet.description:
I'm the creator of both the Groove Dub Techno series and the Atmospheric Dub Techno series (Dark, Deep and Heavy & Ambient and Chill). Please check out my Soundcloud for more.

I do not own any of the tracks, songs or pictures that I use. All rights and ownership belong to the artists who will always be listed in the descriptions or titles of my videos.
My videos are strictly for fun and to help promote the artists used in them. 

Please note: 
It is still my work though,
I do NOT want anyone re-uploading or posting my mixes and calling them their own. If they are re-uploaded/posted by someone (whether on this site or another) I would like credit - make sure to credit all the artists featured too. 
Some mixes are technically more like "compilations" but due to consistency they will all remain titled as "mixes". I am doing my best to improve each set (quality, skill/knowledge etc) with every upload.

Lastly, I do NOT make any money from the ads on my videos. 

Thanks for listening.
